      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INDIANA CANDY (8) resumes after a break of three-and-a-half months. Trying to repeat her debut win over 1200m at Palermo to kick off last prep. Comes to hand quickly so a bold showing is expected. ORPHILA (6) proved too strong last start and scored by 4 lengths over 1200m at this track. Has a decent record at this track with two wins and three minor placings from eight starts. Can measure up again. ESTHETIC CHIC (2) registered a strong win at this track two runs ago. Not disgraced last time out when third over 1600m at this track, beaten 1.75 lengths. Finds a suitable assignment and can rediscover winning form. EN LA RIBERA (3) turned in a decent effort last start to finish second over 1400m at La Plata. Suitably placed so anticipating another big run.",
